name: Gwyneth Paltrow
description:
Gwyneth Kate Paltrow (born September 27, 1972) is an American actress and businesswoman. She is the recipient of various accolades, including an Academy Award, a Golden Globe Award, and a Primetime Emmy Award.

If you like my work, a review is more than welcome! Also, follow me on Twitter or Instagram!

Looking for something... spicy? Here's my Patreon!

Also, I recently started a blog where I will gather resources and tutorials about my work here!

Hello there! Today I present you my textual inversion of Gwyneth Paltrow. I used 60 public images of her (30 close portraits, 30 half-lenght), with an 8200 steps process. Hope you'll like it!

To use it in your works:

  • download the file and place it into stable-diffusion-webui>embeddings folder;

  • add gwypaltrow72 to your prompt;

  • keep the sampling steps around 30, and CFG between 6 and 8 to work well. Great results with DPM++ SDE Karras & Realistic Vision. Face restore could help sometimes, especially when the image is not a close-up/portrait;
